<i>adjective</i>: 고약하다 [고ː야카다], 고약스럽다 [고ː약쓰럽따] <i>determiner</i>: 고얀 [고ː얀] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>고약하다 [고ː야카다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bad; nasty; disgusting</dd><br>
<dd>맛, 냄새 등이 역하거나 매우 좋지 않다.</dd><br>
<dd>A taste, smell, etc., being disgusting or awful.</dd><br>
<dd>2. bad; ugly; bitter</dd><br>
<dd>얼굴 생김새나 표정 등이 흉하거나 험상궂다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's looks, facial expression, etc., being ugly or tough.</dd><br>
<dd>3. ill-natured; wicked; malicious</dd><br>
<dd>버릇이나 성격, 언행 등이 사납고 못되다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's habit, personality, speech, behavior, etc., being rough and bad.</dd><br>
<dd>4. bad; nasty; horrible</dd><br>
<dd>인심이 도리에 벗어난 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>The mind of ordinary people being not generous.</dd><br>
<dd>5. bad; terrible; awful</dd><br>
<dd>날씨가 거칠고 사납다.</dd><br>
<dd>The weather being rough and wild.</dd><br>
<dd>6. hard; troublesome</dd><br>
<dd>일이 꼬여 난처하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Puzzled when something does not work out.</dd><br>
<dt>고약스럽다 [고ː약쓰럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>ill-natured; evil; wicked</dd><br>
<dd>날씨나 사람의 성격이나 언행, 또는 맛과 냄새 등이 나쁜 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>The weather, behavior, or a personality, remark, smell, taste, etc., being bad.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt>고얀 [고ː얀]</dt><br>
<dd>ill-natured; evil; wicked</dd><br>
<dd>성격이나 언행이 아주 못된.</dd><br>
<dd>Personality, words or actions being bad-natured.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>